# Toolchain pin for asdf / mise. Keeps local, CI and teammates on one set of tool
# versions instead of "works on my machine". Each line is `<tool> <version>`.
#
# This is the language-agnostic variant, so nothing is pinned yet - add the tools
# your stack actually uses and keep the versions in sync with the CI workflow.
# Examples (uncomment and set real versions):
#
# nodejs 22.11.0
# python 3.12.6
# golang 1.23.4
# rust 1.83.0
